            In college algebra you might be asked to find the domain of a function like <m>f(x)=sqrt(x^2 - 5)</m>.
            What inequality would you have to solve to determine the domain of <m>f</m>?
          </p>
        </statement>
      </exercise> -->
    </reading-questions>
  
